 not represent clients before any tax authority. Combined county sales-tax rates are framed qualitatively &mdash; confirm any figure against the <a href="https://www.ncdor.gov/taxes-forms/sales-and-use-tax/sales-and-use-tax-rates/current-sales-and-use-tax-rates" rel="noopener nofollow">North Carolina Department of Revenue rate chart</a> and your CPA.</p>
